<item>
            <title>[HBASE-3174] Add ability for Get operations to enable/disable use of block caching</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/HBASE-3174</link>
                <project id="12310753" key="HBASE">HBase</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;The public Get API does not currently support enabling/disabling the block cache like Scans do.  No reason they shouldn&apos;t and now that they get converted into Scans this should be fairly trivial.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
                <environment></environment>
        <key id="12478705">HBASE-3174</key>
            <summary>Add ability for Get operations to enable/disable use of block caching</summary>
